# AudioFileStreamPropertyID

**Type Alias**

Uniquely identifies an audio file stream property.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias AudioFileStreamPropertyID = UInt32
```

## Discussion

See [doc://com.apple.audiotoolbox/documentation/AudioToolbox/1391506-audio-file-stream-properties] for possible values.

## Data Types

- **AudioFileStreamID**: Defines an opaque data type that represents an audio file stream parser.
